OK! Let me explain this to you... The reason why you got the whole game out of any file you tried to extract was that you still had all the rar-files in the same folder. If you had copied ONE rar-file to another folder, you would have gotten a request or the rest of the files. The reason for this is that the rar's are built together in a structure, and it always starts at volume 1. If this , or any other file, is missing, you won't be able to unpack it. So no... there's NO way around the 6 gig download, sorry...
